      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six paired with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual. This example boasts unparalleled mechanical integrity; the rod bearing service and VANOS overhaul are documented, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with factory precision. The chassis is flawless, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a perfectly dialed-in limited-slip differential. Finished in its original factory coat with zero clear-coat degradation, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated BMW engineering for the discerning collector.",
